{"type": "article", "id": 59573, "title": "今年份的圣诞橱窗大赏，好玩又好吃｜这个设计了不起", "description": "每个周末，《好奇心日报》都会找个主题为你寻找精彩设计。", "date": "2018-12-21T22:46:32Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 3919, "name": "橱窗设计"}, {"id": 19968, "name": "装置设计"}, {"id": 21838, "name": "Bergdorf Goodman"}, {"id": 3333, "name": "Harvey Nichols"}, {"id": 315, "name": "Selfridges"}, {"id": 55319, "name": "Liberty"}, {"id": 48208, "name": "Hermes"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 176, "image": "img/article/article_show/20181221202354kns0y32ude1SMDEH.gif", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><p>圣诞将近，最受瞩目的莫过于照亮整个城市的各国百货公司圣诞橱窗。各大百货的圣诞橱窗秀，都已经成为一年一度的视觉狂欢，每当橱窗秀揭幕的时候，都会引发无数人的围观。而在国内，近年来商场在圣诞主题橱窗上，也越来越愿意下功夫。</p><p>这个周末，我们盘点了一组今年的圣诞橱窗，一起来看看。</p><h3>Hermes2018 圣诞橱窗</h3><p>随着浓郁的节日气氛来临，上海“爱马仕之家”也揭开了圣诞的温暖序幕。艺术家陆平原先生受邀创作冬季主题橱窗，并将橱窗概念延展至四楼展览空间，以《箱中奇遇》个人艺术展全面呈献趣致盎然的美学故事。</p><p>受到各类动画作品的启发，陆平原认为孩子的想象力更为大胆广阔，“玩”的过程便是一场最珍贵的艺术创作。他从爱马仕年题“尽情趣玩”中发现童年的创造力，尤其是孩子对玩具进行自由的重构，由此展现让想象力任意驰骋的创造行为。</p><p>以此为灵感，冬季主题橱窗展现了一系列具有颠覆性的、用玩具拼贴的作品。每个橱窗中都代入了一个特立独行的孩子，他们尽情地把爱马仕服饰和家具都捣腾一遍，根据疯狂的想象再次重组。</p><p>女性世界橱窗展现了过家家游戏中喜剧化的场景，每一个物件都来自女孩的玩具盒，他们有着统一的色调和风格，代表着女孩井井有条的游戏。男性世界橱窗则被打造成一个男孩艺术家的疯狂工作室，用惊人的创造力拆卸和重组各种玩具，形成各种雕塑作品一般的物件。现实与虚构交错的叙事方式展现出一种新的审美趣味，创造出幽默、欢乐、充满想象力的故事。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181221202425htm3Axi1I59DnkWZ.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563014\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181221202425fh1v8kBEeTl6RQnw.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563014\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181221202426jz8SNiH6QqIRcPLm.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563014\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181221202427yXZ5kKO4wAfHsLoP.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.512848\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201812212024280vqzuNQfBIDCE3XV.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.903320\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181221202428U8B2yeqDp3Q9oYAL.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.483333\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181221202431miFko4e5L6RwOdrj.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563014\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181221202431zcS76a1b8NLGOnve.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563014\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>伦敦 Liberty 百货 2018 圣诞橱窗</h3><p>被誉为“伦敦最美百货商场”的 Liberty 百货刚刚换上圣诞新装，还请来了许多“小动物”一同参加圣诞庆典，一起装饰圣诞橱窗。Liberty 百货面料印花设计师 Fion Griffith 和新锐诗人 Gabrielle Djanogly 共同完成了今年 Liberty 百货的圣诞主题“Liberty圣诞故事”（The Liberty Christmas Story）。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181221202737KAMTsk6tUyCOYjFx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181221202738jCJdvfpQGrWmgx3t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.152344\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181221202739CHVPveoDLXbBzZ3Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666327\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201812212027426IJwgLyh7GHuXnQt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.housebeautiful.com/uk/lifestyle/a24685140/liberty-london-christmas-windows/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Housebeautiful</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>伦敦 Selfridges 百货 2018 圣诞橱窗</h3><p>Selfridges 百货早在今年 8 月就提前推出了圣诞商店和圣诞系列商品，也是伦敦最早换上圣诞新装的百货商场。Selfridges 百货今年的圣诞主题是“Selfridges摇滚过圣诞”（Selfridges Rocks Christmas），一系列闪亮夺目的时尚单品，助你创造摇滚巨星般的造型，成为圣诞派对上的明星。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181221203448JypqdEtlQnj8X7BT.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.234443\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181221203449PQupjDXmn2MlUtNF.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.658333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181221203449BWiEUwFj7PNHO9to.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.658333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181221203450i9atPjuGcQoVhRHr.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.658333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018122120345112e5qKLOYhXFSAzy.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.234443\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181221203451JX4HPtz9nvSNTEka.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.658333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.selfridges.com/QA/en/features/articles/christmas/windows#\" rel=\"nofollow\">Selfridges</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Harrods 百货 2018 圣诞橱窗</h3><p>今年圣诞，如果你去伦敦旅游购物，Harrods 百货绝对是不容错过的一站。今年，Harrods 百货的圣诞主题是“梦幻盛宴”（Fantastica），店内的每个角落都会有惊喜等着你。店外的 Hans Crescent 小广场上还竖起了一棵八米高的圣诞树，上面装饰着上百个以食物主题的挂饰，快来找找有没有你最爱的圣诞美食吧。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181221203846CqmQY6MBFGWpTj1J.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201812212038488CxYorDHyAEVlf16.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181221203848sSXm6dkrEg4MxKv8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181221203849Fl05dnUYqRaCD8pI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.497396\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181221203850HL36RjmxZ4J8MYsv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.497396\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181221203900cfCM9yWxp7lNhmdg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.housebeautiful.com/uk/lifestyle/a24850770/harrods-christmas-window-displays/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Housebeautiful</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Harvey Nichols 百货 2018 圣诞橱窗</h3><p>Harvey Nichols 百货一直以前卫设计和新锐风格著称，今年的圣诞橱窗也很有想象力。一瓶巨大的香槟喷洒出金色和银色的金属亮片，换上圣诞派对华服的模特在流光溢彩中翩翩起舞，尽情享受节日季节的欢快气氛。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181221215006YnV8pPDf4ZxCkTbQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.675000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181221215007v4giAXHhu2zD8Yw5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.663333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181221215007XYIPdOe34KqJ16T0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.646667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181221215008CKsimpRgd8BAnq70.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.501667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Bergdorf Goodman 2018 圣诞橱窗</h3><p>纽约奢侈品百货商店 Bergdorf Goodman 的橱窗应该是足够好吃了，这也是唯一一组让人看上去很饿的圣诞橱窗。</p><p>一组橱窗的主题是姜饼，整组橱窗色系全部用姜饼的颜色组成，和各种类型的蛋糕组合搭配，场景统一性很高，质感处理得很逼真。</p><p>另一组设计主要在模特的头部做文章，把所有的模特头都换成了糖果、甜甜圈。</p><p>设计师在制作过程中为了让道具看上去像真的糖果，光是喷漆就耗费了一周的时间。还有一组硬质糖果的主题，橱窗背景处的动画浮雕和模特身上的新品是同一个系列，在玩转趣味性的同时也没有放过推广新品。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181221220200Zh5Xen9J01cPOtdQ.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714063\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181221220202uwaFJAnyQ1vx7Xcd.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.918750\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181221220202P7FOTEnpBjibfNIQ.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.738462\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181221220203eVa958Zd42TbM6GO.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.433333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181221220204vnwFUdgq3WMY7BJK.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.327434\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201812212202050HJ7pdzSjqPxaWlm.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.167188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181221220205sx0VHum2wIG5LzZo.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.171875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181221220206ZCcota29hYwIKXkq.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.998437\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201812212202067bLBX9EqIctd6zFf.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.925000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181221220207EZm50PU2fXAV4lKa.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.923438\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}